THIS IS THE CHANGELOG OF THE "BoneProfileR" PACKAGE

            CHANGES IN VERSION 4.0 (2025-07-07)

* New online version - 4.0 (2025-04-18)

            CHANGES IN VERSION 3.3 (2025-04-18)

* Main check version to validate outputs - 3.2 (2024-08-24)
* Better check for partial reading - 3.2.1 (2024-12-11)
* Better check tif reading - 3.2.2 (2024-12-12)
* Correct the grid for partial slides - 3.2.3 (2024-12-12)
* New periodic model - 3.2.4 (2024-12-30)
* Big update and bug correction - 3.2.5 (2025-01-02)
* Acceleration of flexit model - 3.2.6 (2025-01-02)
* MCMC for periodic model - 3.2.7 (2025-01-03)
* New options for plot - 3.2.8 (2025-01-10)
* Correct a bug in radial analysis in Windows - 3.2.9 (2025-01-13)
* Numerous checked sections and minor changes to make it more robust - 3.3 (2025-04-18)

            CHANGES IN VERSION 3.1.1 (2024-11-19)
            
* Preliminary version 3.0 that uses grayscale gradient - 3.0 (2024-07-21)
* New algoritm to determine the contour of section with very irregular shape (thanks to Stephanie Baumgart to have identified this problem) - 3.0 (2024-08-22)
* New algoritm to determine the radial compactness - 3.0 (2024-08-22)
* New parameter method to generate convex section - 3.1 (2024-08-24)

            CHANGES IN VERSION 2.5 (2022-09-06)
            
* Accelerate treatment x30 for center detection and compactness analysis - 2.5 (2024-04-10)
* New references - 2.5 (2024-04-10)
* Correct a rare error that produce non-convergence - 2.5.1 (2024-07-09)
* Correct error in the output of BP_ChooseForeground() - 2.5.2 (2024-04-10)

            CHANGES IN VERSION 2.4 (2022-09-06)
            
* New CRAN version - 2.4 (2022-09-06)

            CHANGES IN VERSION 2.3-3 (2022-08-22)
            
* New CRAN version - 2.3 (2022-07-14)
* align parameter for html5 is removed - 2.3-3 (2022-08-22)

            CHANGES IN VERSION 2.2-7 (2022-05-06)
            
* New CRAN version - 2.2 (2022-04-04)
* Minor change for class management - 2.2-1 (2022-04-20)
* Update to use HelpersMG 5.3-1 - 2.2-5 (2022-05-02)
* Correct a bug in shiny package  - 2.2-6 (2022-05-06)

            CHANGES IN VERSION 2.1-1 (2022-04-02)
            
* New CRAN version - 2.1 (2022-03-04)
* Check update at startup 2.1-2 (2022-04-02)

            CHANGES IN VERSION 2.0-7 (2022-03-04)
            
* First CRAN version - 2.0 (2021-10-05)
* Can fit bone section with very large K1 or K2 values in flexit model - 2.0-1 (2021-10-12)
* Minor change for figures in documentation - 2.0-2 (2022-02-17)
* New option for plot: colors to show histogram of colors - 2.0-3 (2022-02-24)
* Bug in BP_ChooseBackground() is corrected - 2.0-3 (2022-02-24)
* New url to update the package before to be uploaded to CRAN - 2.0-5 (2022-03-03)
* Minor change in documentation - 2.0-6 (2022-03-03)
* New option for plot: 3Dcolors to show 3D graph of colors - 2.0-8 (2022-03-04)

            CHANGES IN VERSIONS 1.x (2020-04-01 to 2021-01-06)
            
* The report include the global compacity - 1.0.2 (2020-04-01)
* Use the new Results managment from HelpersMG - 1.1 (2020-04-20)
* New functions BP_GetFittedParameters(), BP_ListAnalyses() - 1.2 (2020-04-22)
* New parameter rotation.angle in BP_EstimateCompactness() - 1.2 (2020-04-23)
* Can use pacakges ijtiff - 1.3 (2020-05-01)
* Use the results manager of HelpersMG - 1.4 (2020-06-01)
* Solve a problem with ijtiff - 1.4.1 (2020-06-08)
* Solve a problem with BP_report - 1.4.1 (2020-06-08)
* BP_report reports the observed and modeled compactness - 1.4.2 (2020-06-08)
* BP_report reports modeled compactness for radial analysis - 1.4.3 (2020-06-09)
* BP_AutoFit to simplify the analysis - 1.4.4 (2020-06-10)
* BP_report reports modeled compactness for radial analysis - 1.4.5 (2020-06-15)
* BP_LnLCompactness is less sensitive to strange data - 1.4.6 (2020-06-17)
* BP_Report report both global compactness by ML and MCMC - 1.4.7 (2020-06-19)
* Tentative to introduce the ontogenic center - 1.4.8 (2020-06-20)
* Shiny application BP - 1.4.9 & 1.4.10 (2020-06-20)
* Use of constrainted fit rater than logit for Min and Max - 1.5 (2020-09-05)
* Web version uses a 2-step fit - 1.5 (2020-09-05)
* Parallel version for radial estimate - 1.6 (2020-09-06)
* 2-steps fit is available for Web and GUI version - 1.6.1 (2020-09-07)
* Bug in Web version - 1.6.2 (2020-09-14)
* plot can plot the model or observation for only one angle - 1.6.3 (2020-09-16)
* axis changed when radial plot is used - 1.6.4 (2020-09-18)
* Correct a bug related to the way R 4.0 handled [ - 1.6.5 (2021-01-06)
* type can be mcmc from plot - 2.0 (2021-09-20)

            CHANGES IN VERSIONS <1 (2020-02-21)

* New package BoneProfileR - 0.1
* First version for test - 0.2
* New function BP_Report() - 0.3
* Polishing - 0.4
* Confidence interval using Hessian matrix is implemented - 0.5
* The mcmc analysis is stored within an analysis - 0.5
* Add the xlsx report - 0.6
* Add a timestamp for the analyses - 0.7
* Correct the estimate of distance to the peripherie - 0.8
* Analysis of partial section - 0.9
* First complete version for tests - 1
